beer.beer_description: Introducing Cherry Mary-Jane in her explosive debut, Cherry BOMG (Beaker Oh My God). She’s bringing a heavy hit of dank, weed-like terpenes and a massive payload of cherry aroma. It’s a serious pucker-fest - properly sour and unapologetically red. She’s wandering the galaxy looking for love and we think Blueberry Jerry might just be her soulmate. Will they meet? Who knows. But until then, she’s here to blow your mind.
